loggers created by this factory will apply this filter.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public LoggerFactory AddFilter(ILogFilter filter)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>filter</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogFilter.html'>ILogFilter</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The filter to add.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.html'>LoggerFactory</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">This factory for fluent chaining.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.AddOutput(Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogOutput)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.AddOutput(Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogOutput)' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_LoggerFactory_AddOutput_Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Abstractions_ILogOutput_'>AddOutput(ILogOutput)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/LoggerFactory.cs#L117'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Adds a log output to this factory.\nAll loggers created by this factory will write to this output.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public LoggerFactory AddOutput(ILogOutput output)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>output</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogOutput.html'>ILogOutput</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The output to add.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.html'>LoggerFactory</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">This factory for fluent chaining.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.CreateLogger(System.String)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.CreateLogger(System.String)' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_LoggerFactory_CreateLogger_System_String_'>CreateLogger(string)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/LoggerFactory.cs#L174'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Creates a new logger instance with the given name.\nThe logger will use all configured outputs, filters, and formatter.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public ILogger CreateLogger(string name)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>name</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The name for the logger (typically a class or component name).</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogger.html'>ILogger</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">A configured ILogger instance.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.Dispose' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.Dispose' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_LoggerFactory_Dispose'>Dispose()    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/LoggerFactory.cs#L83'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Disposes this instance</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>[ExcludeFromCodeCoverage]\npublic void Dispose()</code></pre><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.Flush' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.Flush' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_LoggerFactory_Flush'>Flush()    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/LoggerFactory.cs#L183'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Flushes all outputs and cleans up resources.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>[ExcludeFromCodeCoverage]\npublic void Flush()</code></pre><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.SetFormatter(Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogFormatter)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.SetFormatter(Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogFormatter)' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_LoggerFactory_SetFormatter_Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Abstractions_ILogFormatter_'>SetFormatter(ILogFormatter)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/LoggerFactory.cs#L151'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Sets the log formatter for this factory.\nAll loggers created by this factory will use this formatter.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public LoggerFactory SetFormatter(ILogFormatter formatter)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>formatter</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogFormatter.html'>ILogFormatter</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The formatter to use.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.html'>LoggerFactory</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">This factory for fluent chaining.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.SetMinimumLevel(Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.LogLevel)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.SetMinimumLevel(Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.LogLevel)' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_LoggerFactory_SetMinimumLevel_Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Abstractions_LogLevel_'>SetMinimumLevel(LogLevel)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/LoggerFactory.cs#L162'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Sets the minimum log level for all loggers created by this factory.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public LoggerFactory SetMinimumLevel(LogLevel level)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>level</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.LogLevel.html'>LogLevel</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The minimum level.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.html'>LoggerFactory</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.LoggerFactory.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">This factory for fluent chaining.</p>\n\r\